sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe / ModelMesh<br/>Platform Gateway
    participant HTTP as Caikit HTTP Server<br/>8080/TCP TLS (configurable)
    participant gRPC as Caikit gRPC Server<br/>8085/TCP mTLS (configurable)
    participant LocalModel as Local Model<br/>(HF Transformers / sentence-transformers)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Server<br/>8033-8034/TCP gRPC TLS/mTLS
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>PVC / S3
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,HTTP: Flow 1: Local Text Generation
        Client->>KServe: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>Platform Auth
        KServe->>HTTP: Forward request<br/>TLS (configurable)
        HTTP->>LocalModel: In-memory inference<br/>(HFAutoCausalLM / HFAutoSeq2SeqLM)
        LocalModel-->>HTTP: Generated text
        HTTP-->>KServe: JSON Response
        KServe-->>Client: Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 2: Remote TGIS Text Generation
        Client->>KServe: gRPC TextGeneration request
        KServe->>gRPC: Forward (mTLS configurable)<br/>Certificate-based auth
        gRPC->>TGIS: gRPC generation request<br/>TLS/mTLS (configurable)
        TGIS-->>gRPC: Generated text response
        gRPC-->>KServe: gRPC response
        KServe-->>Client: Response
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,LocalModel: Flow 3: Text Embedding
        Client->>KServe: POST /api/v1/task/embedding<br/>or gRPC Embedding
        KServe->>HTTP: Forward request
        HTTP->>LocalModel: sentence-transformers<br/>In-memory embedding
        LocalModel-->>HTTP: Embedding vectors
        HTTP-->>KServe: JSON Response
        KServe-->>Client: Embedding response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over Client,Storage: Flow 4: PEFT Prompt Tuning (Training)
        Client->>gRPC: Training request<br/>mTLS Certificate-based
        gRPC->>LocalModel: PyTorch PEFT training<br/>In-memory (GPU)
        LocalModel->>Storage: Save tuned prompts<br/>Filesystem
        LocalModel-->>gRPC: Training complete
        gRPC-->>Client: Training response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 230)
        Note over HTTP,HFHub: Model Download (Optional)
        HTTP->>HFHub: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443 / API token
        HFHub-->>HTTP: Model files
        HTTP->>Storage: Cache model artifacts
    end
